data.description: This beautiful like new townhome is in the Emerson community of  Crawford Creek. As you enter the home you will notice the open floor plan.  Each bedroom with its own bathroom along with large closets and plenty of storage space.  Seller is leaving a new refrigerator as well as a new Whirl Pool washer and dryer. This is a perfect home for entertaining with your covered patio for grilling. The  front porch is also coverd. There is a $165 monthly fee which covers water for front sprinklers, front lawn care, trash service,  insect spray and maintance to the front of the home.  This home is a must see!  Amendities include two pools, tennis courts, pickle ball courts and playgrounds.  perfect neighborhood for the up and coming!!
